Currency Exchange Rates
- Ugandan Shillings (UGX) to US Dollars (USD): The current exchange rate for UGX to USD stands at 1 USD = 3,722.14 UGX ¹. This exchange rate is subject to fluctuations and may change.
- US Dollars (USD) to Ugandan Shillings (UGX): Conversely, the exchange rate for USD to UGX stands at 1 UGX = 0.00026866244 USD ¹.
- Currency Exchange Rate Volatility: The exchange rates for UGX to USD and USD to UGX have fluctuated between highs and lows over the last 30 and 90-day periods, with an average exchange rate of 0.00026890 and 0.00026734, respectively ¹.
- Currency Exchange Market: Currency exchange markets are open 24 hours a day on weekdays, which means the best time to buy Uganda Shillings is any day of the week except on weekends ².
